			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Adam, it&#8217;s possible that transaction costs are <em>lower</em> in autocracies, other things equal, because of the existence of the &#8220;<strong>particular</strong> coalitions&#8221; you cite. It&#8217;s more clear who you have to pay off.</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

