			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>It&#8217;s possible, but I doubt it. It just depends on which transaction costs you&#8217;re talking about, of course. I&#8217;m talking about the transaction costs borne of the shift from one coalition in power to another; in democracies that involves leaving office and taking office, in other systems it usually involves bloodshed.</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

